{"tid":619540,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人一諗到死亡就好驚？","createTime":"2018-04-06T17:30:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T20:06:09.000Z","uid":9532,"like":35,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"c427a4ab9e1ee904d538e26b0e464a617bb463e5","tid":619540,"uid":9532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T17:30:31.000Z","msg":"人一出世就係不停向死亡靠近<br />\n就算唔係後生意外死都好<br />\n老死都好似會有一種遺憾<br />\n會唔捨得身邊既人同事<br />\n而且絕大部份死亡過程都係痛苦<br />\n一諗到自己有一日會死就覺得好驚<br />\n有冇人都係咁？<br />\n<br />\n利申 無神論者 相信死後只會變成一堆冇生命力既元素"},{"pid":"8a98cf4d0f55ecec32b91cbf6e7fc4409377a3d2","tid":619540,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T17:33:43.000Z","msg":"人生只係一件事 做完一件事 就會結束"},{"pid":"7968f9a0942a13f03f4c4f13e84ca048c43f324a","tid":619540,"uid":133033,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T17:34:33.000Z","msg":"正評係比你最後果句特別既觀點<br />\n驚咪唔好諗 活在當下啦 onnine"},{"pid":"8cd3797be0bb247b578840a05d8234395171dadb","tid":619540,"uid":94255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T17:46:00.000Z","msg":"唔驚，我覺得係有無限輪迴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c29231a98486cfe49f84318866ede7a59cd0319c","tid":619540,"uid":34394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T17:47:24.000Z","msg":"咁係因為樓主你人生有意義<br />\n聽到死<br />\n我就好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8243783658cd06b0253284bd311f419dfbc5d4eb","tid":619540,"uid":165871,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T17:47:45.000Z","msg":"人生就係要係有限既時間入面 去完成自己最想做既事"},{"pid":"6e89989cc7618faa9fa5b9fb3dc211c914089913","tid":619540,"uid":92230,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T17:51:33.000Z","msg":"死亡係唯一解答到所有答案不可知既哲學問題既方法<br />\n<br />\n所以唔會, 我唔會好驚"},{"pid":"e9b3fce19059e77e36cba64260bddfd3e2c9cb79","tid":619540,"uid":9532,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8cd3797be0bb247b578840a05d8234395